5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","Springwood"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in Springwood? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across Springwood, Underwood, Slacks Creek and Daisy Hill. Our 5-star instructors help Springwood students pass their Queensland driving test on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Springwood is a significant commercial and residential hub on the southern motorway corridor, best known for its substantial retail and business precinct at Springwood Road and Rochedale Road. The Springwood CBD precinct is one of Logan's most active commercial areas — featuring major supermarkets, retail complexes, and high pedestrian activity throughout the day. For learner drivers, this environment provides authentic urban driving and car park application training that directly transfers to the Queensland practical assessment."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"The Pacific Motorway (M1) defines the suburb's western boundary with the associated service roads and interchanges providing excellent motorway-adjacent training. Our instructors use the Springfield Road Bridge overpass and the associated service road network here as the key motorway confidence building environment — structured, familiar, and progressively challenging across multiple lessons."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Springwood learners test at the Browns Plains Transport and Main Roads Centre. Free pickup from Springwood, modern automatic vehicles, Afterpay available. Book your lesson today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","